      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This collector-grade E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated Bavarian engineering. Under the hood lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a forged steel crankshaft, capable of an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed via a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock. This example is mechanically impeccable: the high-pressure VANOS system has been fully serviced, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications with refreshed bushings and dampers, providing the precise feedback and lateral grip expected of this chassis. This is a zero-compromise, turn-key example for the discerning driver.",
